    - DEX → +Stamina Regen (Need_Stamina.NeedInterval)
    - STR → +Might damage (mightPwr)
    - DEX → -Might cooldown, -Stamina cost
    - WIS → +Magic damage (arcaneDmg), -Mana cost
    - INT → -Magic cooldown, +Psionic max
    - VIT → +Chi max (Monk)
